POP'SCIENCES

   https://popsciences.universite-lyon.fr/
   Sharing knowledge, opening campuses!
   The portal, which was designed and organized by the Université de Lyon,
   its members and its key partners, has a number of functions:
     * A calendar for cultural events relating to science and technology
       in Metropolitan Lyon and Rhône,
     * A multimedia resource bank with questions about all topics in
       science and technology
     * A catalogue of offers and teaching resources for students, provided
       by the UdL's member and associated institutions.

Discover the Pop'Sciences portal

   IFRAME: //www.youtube.com/embed/Qm-prNOXepo

